Benefits
The main advantage of converting loans into CHF in lei is that the currency risk is eliminated, the consumer is protected from future increases in the franc, and the loan is repaid in the currency in which he earns his salary.
Another major advantage of both conversion offers is that no re-evaluation of the property is required, no additional collateral is required and no other proof of income is required.
In practice, there will be no new financial and legal analysis of the loan, nor will there be any additional costs as in the case of a refinancing.
